p.k: Let It Snowball Seth wants to bring snow home so it'll earn him a coveted spot on his mom's prized shelf of stuff her kids gave her. When he repeatedly tries and fails to bring the snow back before it melts he uses science to figure out a way to get it home intact.
p.d: This prehistoric comedy from Stephen Neary explores Fungietown through the whimsical quests of Seth, a young student at Fungietown Elementary.
